Usage:
Copy the COCCAReg folder to YOUR_WHMCS_ROOT/modules/addons
Copy the COCCAepp folder to YOUR_WHMCS_ROOT/modules/registrars

Login to WHMCS as an administrator and go to Setup->Addon Modules

Activate the COCCA Registrar Manager

Go to Setup->Products/Services->Domain Registrars and activate the module COCCAepp.

Click on configure... Select the SSL option and enter the certificate path. (The only necessary setting here

Go to Addons and select COCCA Registrar Manager option

Click on the Add new tab and enter the details about the registry. Add as many registry settings as required


